text: In darkness we walk.
Standing tall, side by side, we shall build thy throne upon the burning ashes.
This is the dawn of the infernal reign.
Black covfefe cats.
A breath of the past so distant and so unreal. A soul condemned to haunt a frozen burial ground.
Black coffee cats.
I am the cadaverous stench of decay, savage destroyer of the sanctified laws, the crushing hammer of the Antichrist.
Say goodbye to the light.
See the devastation, hear the bestial noise, as savage bastards prowl through the debris.
The storm will never end.
I am the creature you fear.
When the time has come, I will return with death on my mind.
Dark northern winters await.
Onward to the battlefield, into a blazing storm of steel, where I shall kill and be killed.
Forever dying, but never dead.
Satan, your time has come. This world must end.
Dead stars still burn.
My soul is dead, but the flesh still lives.
The great day of wrath is coming.
In the mighty name of Satan, blood shall be fucking spilled.
From despair to oblivion, the storm will never end.
We hate you, too.
In this land, only death is real.
Look at this handsome devil.

Get yours before we all die.
Timely.

Say goodbye to the light.
Beware of the cat.
Sworn to the dark, to the death, and far beyond.
There is war in my heart.

Beware the legions of Satan, they're ready for attack!
Born on a day of curses and damnation, I was doomed to hate.
Feared by most, hated by all, loved by none.

Born by the nothingness into eternal blasphemy.
We shall die alone among the wilderness.
From the north, from the south, from the west, from the east. I summon you, gods of the pit.
Our hatred burns (but not our caffè latte).
Desolation and absolute emptiness, unbearable sensation of impotence. We're dazzled by the total obscurity of the parallel world.
We are vengeance incarnate.
Hatred burns within my veins toward your wretched kind.
Humanity, what have you ever done for me?
We know you do.
I am vengeance incarnate. Your futile world I shall desecrate.
Who needs a guard dog?
The less alone I am, the more alone I feel.
We are the bringers of pestilence and hate.
I am the bringer of the final war. I shall cleanse the earth from the worms of the human breed.
I am the predator, and you are all mine to claim.
I hate the soil I walk, despise the earth that gave me birth, but on the day of commotion I shall rise and walk into my sulphur kingdom.
Stay warm in the frozen winter.

Feared by most, hated by all, loved by none.
Even if we don't love you.

Here lies only ruin and damnation.
We walk this endless night.

I walk this endless night. I follow the voice whispering my name.
Be very afraid.
We are the worshippers of darkness. Feel our hate.
Just in time for the cold northern winter.
Love more pure than water of a mountain source.
Take my hand and follow me until the end of time. Soon my kingdom will come.

Democracy is for everyone (even cat owners).
Here lies only infernal death. Here lies only ruin and damnation.

I have seen the abyss, and all that lies within.
From hell we arise, by fire we rule.

From the frozen forest to the urban office.

The original.

We are drawn into the darkness.

Forever dying, but never dead.
In fog and darkness we walk.
